{"h46773966gb0c3g4bdfgbcb6g2c3cfe3ba1b6": ["Home!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "b958ba9b-5097-25d9-2868-875c207856ae"], "hc0429460ga087g4ea8g90c0g6f88eae4f78d": ["<i>Pet him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "cbd9cf0e-778b-d7ff-915e-51633cedf0bd"], "h57215ad5g0e65g4fcfgb74eg091a58444ef0": ["Friend. Nice. No bite!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "c1252e33-0acf-21a0-f160-21373585485a"], "h87cd3fb3g69fdg44ffgb52cgb68da5f2b857": ["*He purrs and chirps, utterly content in your presence.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "d08897f9-0c2b-3873-4a98-4ca9c0728b03"], "h815975baga531g4e94gb706g92ab418b46fe": ["*Coo.*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "66e4fb33-df57-2abf-8c15-e31c6b26b9df"], "h5fccfce0g816cg4926g97d2g5db221388cc0": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "74a0c241-2037-f07a-3d4d-a891cc7e3e2e"], "h76bbe63eg19cbg45d3gb09ag0d58708798e9": ["*The cub chirps brightly in recognition.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "d0bea22a-9ede-27f1-a512-8ffd05c66e61"], "h32f59f7cg7b91g486bg9e4cgd2cb9499dbaa": ["*Chirrup!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "9a822e32-9de8-5d33-db35-2bdc270b43ad"], "h898226f8g039bg4c2dg9e16g13113d91bbba": ["Food! Gift!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "e6528576-6066-07b4-7fbf-cb94aeba0310"], "h91e449e1gbfb2g49ccgba55g8ac68238e8b0": ["*The cub looks to a mass of feathers on the ground - a dead bird.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "cfb048de-67b2-3d81-4a26-3a9806f1e84a"], "h840f8d15g4d15g4429g94ccg28ff105a599c": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "1da497c0-84ae-c74a-2c8c-266d6bcdb082"], "ha86b0567g83a4g4e55ga514g97f213b7fbbf": ["You eat! You bite!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "be9f3c92-2907-1388-5ed0-41b535da78e8"], "hf29dbefag0668g427bga636g7c74d8afd5b6": ["I am <i>not</i> eating that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "937302f6-02f2-2f34-0d2e-fe9350e266e4"], "h0fb2f33dgb3adg4fbcg86d3gd2e5c01dd173": ["No want? Hate me...", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "aeb98884-e68e-a4b3-f9f2-0d765909f364"], "hf160e68agbb63g4f71g942cg69a3dc70e7fa": ["You should have it - so you grow big and strong.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "f1ea1507-1679-8796-d90f-3d1391f8cde2"], "h891df141g6027g4363g8001g710a7a12b069": ["EAT!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "82280055-e645-fc1a-692e-37617a5d1317"], "hf3f6ff79g43aeg487cg9752gaa464ae8c1ec": ["*The cub tears into the bird with ravenous abandon.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "17a4c262-26e1-092f-d8a9-4ee61310e387"], "hee671442g2103g4749ga53eg92efe1c2df1a": ["Brilliant. Now we'll never be rid of it.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "10894870-1e16-a0f7-dc04-ba3cf3ca217a"], "h9072acdbgf190g4be5gac5dgd25dd88cf726": ["The little beast's quite charming once you get accustomed to the smell of rotting flesh.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "81607b48-82a7-34f4-6414-7bf21e3ec2cd"], "h818bd8bdg8d6eg4dc8gad7dgc1379f7dee63": ["|I like this thing.|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "a681f2ce-8e2b-d5ac-c9f6-59be3da6e72f"], "h95c0f0f3g8795g428fg8ba8g5f3b5a1835d3": ["|New friend! New friend! New! Friend!|", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "e90a22e0-6937-7168-03d9-d336962545b2"], "hcd3a5318g090eg41c2gb7d2g97d0d040949f": ["Adorable. Let me know when it brings you something fresh.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "c5a7a5bc-19aa-0b26-d817-569c7000d517"], "hba47e82bg943eg49c4gb4e7g0ac3e6798518": ["|WEREWORLF!|", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "0c31073d-c1eb-668b-1716-b3163707040a"], "h7219e16cgf4c8g4242ga12ag400c79105d54": ["Cute. Till it grows up and gnaws your arm off, at least.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "22ba9a0b-7068-f384-58cf-66da3d3fbccd"], "ha86d84deg0670g40e1gbe9eg44b4005d235a": ["You do realise these things grow, do you not? Teeth and talons first.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "080710bb-dbdc-0b20-a3f8-fb688336d924"], "h284915bag843dg46a5ga6c1g240474c02865": ["No bite! Friend! Safe!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "728d6bfb-91b0-3d72-de37-436e2e262b70"], "h95429bd7g3c36g4868gb492g069c97d78668": ["*The creature coos happily - he feels safe.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "13337e6e-f25b-e39a-1813-c49c768372ab"], "h5b0fea7cgd508g4b12g8f08g82c22a7dfbf4": ["*Coo!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "69eaf66b-6666-b0cb-65b0-ba13b7c5c7f0"], "h747071feg81b6g416egaefbg989221caf2ff": ["I don't hate you, I'm just saving this for later.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "245a5e58-ab32-996f-e536-118c5d7a26e6"], "hccc320e0g0bf3g40b6ga6b2gf71a5db4a9c4": ["Later? Wait. Wait!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "2d439fbb-f5d5-16c3-3ebb-41876fb5df05"], "h4f421304gd1e0g446dgb581g4bca5b77f86c": ["Hold on, hold on... I'll eat it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "0aaf2ea4-719b-bcc4-3cbf-9829b0447873"], "hf7687badg3630g4946gb411gbbe6e45ff26c": ["*You chew through the bird's rotten flesh, its putrefied organs squishing between your teeth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "4270a8c7-c4aa-7cb6-d974-2971da9e184a"], "h3267d5c6g3a02g438agaa32g515c6b774e59": ["Friend like! EAT!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "e99ddf4a-c029-398b-8de9-1d604d6dd141"], "h31bb46f0g9697g4d15gb262gd6502b7d5f07": ["Fine, you little beast. I'll eat it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "4cf6e91c-64fc-f997-f169-13da3c57dd04"], "h9afe108cg1600g4981gbe00gf673f4116111": ["*The bird's blood is gritty and congealed, giving the meal a rotten chew.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "c666d051-0640-85c1-615f-bfe91e4b7d5c"], "h11862b14g5517g47aega72fg26a24238bd7b": ["That's right. Now get out of my camp.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "265e1f11-621e-907a-e75f-abc280aa4b34"], "h674966a5g006fg4f1cgb349g48d50ebff6c3": ["Mean! Not friend!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "0c85e66c-1413-845f-564d-30e5e36b8b9a"], "h20a5e116g4f92g4badgb4e5ge8f7ca236e0c": ["*Dejected, he plods out of camp and into the forest beyond for the final time.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "4641e467-3e0b-3729-11cd-4dd08301d12f"], "h60455a3fg0908g4ddaga4b0gfd968be782f8": ["<i>Eat the bird.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "2d0afd05-715f-7c58-d8f0-8b2533d5166c"], "h7d831c33gf2b2g410bgb3dbgd317323721c3": ["<i>Sink your teeth into the bird, drinking deeply.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "146dba48-8a3f-a2dc-3504-556dbcfa4d4e"], "h96d8cd26g684dg45a6gac23g710773eab3b9": ["<i>Make a show of eating the bird whole, slipping it into your bag instead.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "48e263cc-c5ef-9357-27c5-e10823aab176"], "h56ec053cg6000g439cgab96gaa7241fab068": ["You look hungry. <i>You </i>should eat it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "9ada74d9-e838-900f-a8d1-af94413d0f5d"], "hc7bc3214gd3ddg4971g89afgfda5814ac791": ["Full? Eat? BITE!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "caddcd94-adbf-e49e-d20d-ee6e4ee9aede"], "h3410053ag4e92g4c44g8d0bg16a41d5abd56": ["<i>Pretend to take a bite of the bird.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "6374256a-59f9-6584-14ea-f0c2a3fddf37"], "h180ed361g139ag4ef4ga2b8g9e78958b8186": ["*You misjudge your bite and end up with a mouthful of dead bird.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "4dbd019c-2c31-b828-f54e-fdd97a56e51a"], "had91e615g5b7bg48c7g86e5gbc0621b8e23b": ["*With a great deal of effort, you manage to swallow the foul meat.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "364fd9f6-bf07-9dc7-ce3b-f382520eff8e"], "h02d48b66g03f0g42eaga111g5512d2194278": ["*You cannot help but spit it back out while the cub watches, indignant.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "6362e330-9f26-2e40-c4f5-0823bcef2584"], "h9f201c39g25cfg4113g8338g16da442b8f89": ["*He looks from the bird to you - it's clear that he wants you to eat it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "b511abf7-baf7-5514-3cad-83a58f3c67bd"], "h2eee93d8g6762g470dga273g69fc57e52c49": ["*Squawk! Hoot!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "2c572b50-07dc-9a32-9a2f-62a9752d059d"], "h84de5634gff67g458ag8b48g812212d6dca7": ["<i>Applaud his catch.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "25f7b63e-cea7-8833-1163-bd6d36673f44"], "h4db9aea0g1bf9g4304g801fgf7a2b2c63060": ["*SQUAWK!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "089d0640-f090-0ac1-3dc6-e17d7885583d"], "hdd6278bcg49d9g4dc5g85f7gcace5ee120f0": ["<i>Figure out what he wants.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "5261f081-579b-98f2-5175-690d66d96c52"], "h273141d5gb935g4313g9831gedcba98cf5c2": ["*A quick gesture of his beak makes it clear - he expects you to eat the bird.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "89d5f4c8-413f-602a-136d-5c215133a26d"], "h0e11f3fbgab46g454eg8943gd0f603e36c6e": ["<i>Scowl - you don't want his dead vermin.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "f97c0752-3f20-7eb2-ec5d-76b081290a90"], "h871e9d06gcbd6g4fcagad7bg9d4fbdc127cb": ["*The cub lets out a quiet squeak - he was proud of his catch.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "944c2bff-9a9b-d27c-02d6-96d669d1d759"], "h3ed0237cgf121g4fbbgbcd6g8d2b00a6bdad": ["*With a sad warble, he skulks out of camp for the last time.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "82504161-a425-5c5c-e1fd-6ce45726b405"], "h7bdb688cga53bg4adcg88a9g5dc115e5d6f2": ["<i>Hold out your hand - he should eat it instead.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "5c091769-c549-ab84-2a95-8a62c3fd7498"], "h74b25695gd18dg41afgb05cg4de3c16332f3": ["*With a delighted hoot, he tears into the dead bird with ravenous abandon.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "6f37dad7-88fe-bf2a-9826-2d27985962b0"], "hd74d888cg3245g4745gb025g976e024d3ccc": ["*Nostrils plugged with clotted blood, he chirps at you affectionately.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "25e994a0-e10d-a254-87fc-9c66ff409624"], "h03f355d1g6deeg4520g9ed1gaf995a9850f0": ["<i>Eat the bird.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "cc1e4934-f072-04d5-3716-daf44b4f7d38"], "h01d3d279g063dg4398gbe3fg9a0b677e5553": ["*Hoo-hoot!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "17d3aa5e-1edb-8b7e-3696-d12cd78d8acb"], "h40d4f152gcd46g445bg99aag82bb7684310d": ["<i>Sink your teeth into the bird, drinking deeply.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "1491788e-2404-ff24-663d-4633dfad39bc"], "h41570826gb87cg48bfgacc7g82bea599ba0a": ["<i>Pretend to swallow it whole and drop it into your bag.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "91cc480a-eeb9-0b7f-ac0b-bf73df1e9a22"], "h0f12e573gc116g423cgbf09g6118471e3e32": ["*You feign shoving the bird into your face, but surreptitiously slip it into your bag.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "4a9bdbc3-b243-14c2-1448-d8aefa3afc3b"], "h5d87860cg2137g40b3ga263ged9bb7ebfd07": ["*You try to slip the bird into your bag, but fumble the move. The carcass falls to the ground with a wet thud.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "33f1cae4-a478-c6ee-219b-ed8ab7c5464c"], "hd889dae6g9cf3g4ebfgb05cgada34949174c": ["*The cub eyes you suspiciously before letting out a sad hoot - he was proud of his catch.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "b1a26f4d-226e-25c3-b39a-0ecbbcf58296"], "hfe8e05a5g3cd5g4a8fgbd97g638cb43b9e4f": ["<i>Pretend to take a bite out of the bird.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "68806372-3339-53d6-4295-2d40a796441d"], "ha582f888geeadg44c2ga1d7g6ae0468dfd7f": ["*The cub hops about, chirping excitedly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "42bba476-2924-d839-84b8-788aec674df7"], "h457f77fag049bg4442g8f23g36509d151664": ["*You misjudged your bite - your teeth sink into the bird's putrid flesh.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "c4ff30b8-5f4d-1721-d0c4-94e851090169"], "he95df35fgde8cg4a94ga97dg540ca9042202": ["*The cub cocks its head slightly, his expectations inscrutable.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "d84bd233-c5b0-3ce3-ea31-c5092a40520b"], "h258f21fcg71d0g44b0g8e75g6bd69aa63f97": ["<i>Enough is enough - attack him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "74ddd220-393e-07ae-629a-99d5a03b6473"], "h6b3b8afbg3178g4129g8144g1219b433ca58": ["<i>Shoo him away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "86a4dbcc-4728-5618-6447-a7d8d7ab6633"], "hc7659957g481fg4c5bg91d3g16aa2155c402": ["*Squeak.*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "c6668ee1-41d2-7618-a6fe-b6a8a7be6f65"], "h571d22dag7ecfg40adg9fa1gabc7e4416320": ["*Hroo-hoot!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "1c2dea5c-4590-f9e6-f6b1-9cb476f301e4"], "h6ab9822dg41a6g4e96gb4d4g1f35f9880a9d": ["*You spot a feathered mass beside the cub - a dead bird.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "244bc82c-073a-e6a9-cc07-78a78573e71d"], "h526e60e0gcc9ag4b35g8d94g2f0a1270d47f": ["Dig. Hide. Dig!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "3ff6de61-70ec-54b1-709f-d8d190ed2333"], "h702dc046gdedbg49b2gbf35g0566b6c39f76": ["You! Run!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "1e5cf9bc-6f02-257e-d999-ffa0b2431e5a"], "hcfc06fd6g5be5g4598ga61egce5423772277": ["That's right. And don't come back!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "24116f92-814b-83ef-0cee-cda398d2777c"], "h3e6f9481g48bcg48a4g951dgf0dcb5d0fae1": ["<i>Block his path.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "ec21ec6b-6fbd-a09e-bb81-30dbc4774dfe"], "h40ff17f7ga2d6g429cgacc8g1514403cb89b": ["Move! BITE!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "156228f1-5492-6148-9098-725cb299643b"], "h624f309fg04ccg4364gbf41g968381b0901c": ["It's all right. You can stay here. It's safe.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "e4559d04-c0ad-8994-544b-ab89699f60aa"], "h7b6fdddeg986eg47cbgaf0aga45c76df4372": ["<i>Meet his threat and attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "f5407689-7a50-99e5-25c2-a99750e95f2e"], "hbea4748bg8eedg48d7g8e70g2918e1dfccb1": ["Stop! Not another step!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "d56d0fa7-b48e-075e-e88d-9490ed4b41d1"], "heaacbebdg8cb0g4992gac3dg18cca7e7baa2": ["Hurt me! No!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "e4c17e95-28ca-1463-030c-4bd5f2aa1393"], "h0bff183fg5c3bg4af1gaa70gd66d03b66e64": ["*SCREECH!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "16b737c4-aa8f-19de-9423-67c26ec451fa"], "h404e6508g9757g4e01gae36g6ee30298272d": ["Wait - I won't hurt you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "04a0b45a-03cb-044e-60e2-093ebd7a9cc1"], "h95e4a01ag9a09g47f1g8ae4gaa291ca47ec2": ["No hurt? Wait!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "aea972e2-c4b3-959c-bf58-5c14ef3ecd7e"], "h84487b05gac9bg4c67gb05dg871d67055e27": ["*Hroo-hoo.*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "f1447cb9-2794-67d9-1519-4c6f194021c3"], "h61b788d0g0723g4ec0gaa11gfd5518e75d65": ["*Squawk!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "7d210b7b-3fcc-e95d-ed18-e0eb8eebd7c6"], "h45f8b36bg5283g41ddgab20g2d85fff0c1d8": ["<i>Move to block his path.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "983c5202-2da2-c038-38d4-0f889e380d69"], "h72ee2ed9ge8b1g4821g8474g0d28d460ac3b": ["*Hroo! Hoo-hoot! Hoo...*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "c0f4c5fb-139d-2df5-03c9-d97ded1fe0ea"], "hd580f56cg85d2g4e25g8245g6f6a76ea42d6": ["*You're too slow - he rushes past you and out of the camp for good.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "3daa5b3e-6df8-d883-b783-37d130ac0e56"], "hc67fed87g5ef8g4a41ga03bgb90fc240a58d": ["<i>Coo at the cub to calm him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "245c761b-e09c-ee88-9261-6e98cbec5dbe"], "hffa0ae33g8789g4dd5ga330gaac815d65d32": ["*The cub's relaxes, soothed by your soft sounds.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "326d5283-c8c6-caf3-a3f2-7ed6e0da6624"], "h5e7769a9gefa0g447egb869gef6a6538089b": ["*With a bright chirp, he moves to the side, revealing a most precious prize: a dead bird.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "bebdb87b-a7f0-64b0-6a24-98453680efb5"], "h2ba06785g0e14g4bcfg9d2cgd56bf0a8504b": ["*SCREECH!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "c129494f-7b2b-9ca6-fb25-911be9d12aa7"], "h51e2f7fag1c78g4946gbf75g6ddf3a0a9600": ["<i>Shrink down to appear nonthreatening.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "ae056cbf-7fe2-3d26-ae2e-27864ace4e44"], "h14bf26fegcd24g4548g966egde05fd256479": ["*Hroo! Hoo-hoot! Hoo...*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "bfa0f340-2254-3260-2c56-853e561919a8"], "h75d814d2gc205g4a70gae2fgffb01362d2f9": ["<i>Attack before he can escape.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "b292934c-3850-10c0-3a8c-ca37f6bd210f"], "hb8f7833ag7f47g4330g997fg9d53f866e925": ["<i>Let him leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_OwlbearCub_CRD_3.html", "e832c1d1-f844-dfb3-dda1-636d7c3b1da6"]}